  "detailed_description": "<i>“You are Rob Riches. Solve the temple mystery!”</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GATHER ALL THE COINS!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/7206ac0fccc606b4a8382108e90de188.poster.avif?t=1683552715\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/7206ac0fccc606b4a8382108e90de188.webm?t=1683552715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/7206ac0fccc606b4a8382108e90de188.mp4?t=1683552715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Your quest? To gather all the coins of course! Solve the puzzle to get each shiny coin, and unlock the path forward.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WATCH YOUR STEP!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/037880e975c50eb73ea26b7bc818f57f.poster.avif?t=1683552715\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/037880e975c50eb73ea26b7bc818f57f.webm?t=1683552715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/037880e975c50eb73ea26b7bc818f57f.mp4?t=1683552715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Some tiles might just fall down, and seal your fate. Make sure you plan ahead in these dangerous temples. In Rob Riches, each step may be your last!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OUT OF MY WAY!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/ebe336f6881f3c39706ab3e25149dff5.poster.avif?t=1683552715\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/ebe336f6881f3c39706ab3e25149dff5.webm?t=1683552715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/ebe336f6881f3c39706ab3e25149dff5.mp4?t=1683552715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>What are all these stones doing here? Some stones can be moved out of the way, use them to protect you or place them on a pressure plate to open a path forward.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IT'S A TRAP!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/ecb158926a1ef9455aa90ed0580b8603.poster.avif?t=1683552715\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/ecb158926a1ef9455aa90ed0580b8603.webm?t=1683552715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/ecb158926a1ef9455aa90ed0580b8603.mp4?t=1683552715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Be careful! Each temple has its own set of traps and dangers you must overcome.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TEST YOUR WIT!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/612d784f6d96f72ebceb4fdecefdbfa5.poster.avif?t=1683552715\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/612d784f6d96f72ebceb4fdecefdbfa5.webm?t=1683552715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/612d784f6d96f72ebceb4fdecefdbfa5.mp4?t=1683552715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As you delve further, the challenges become progressively more difficult to truly test your puzzle solving skills!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CLAIM YOUR PRIZE!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655670/extras/985c1a526bae4ce47d51603382ef9804.avif?t=1683552715\" width=768 height=432 /></span><br><br>Surpass the dangers to claim each world's great treasure - they belong in a museum!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Nearly <strong>100</strong> unique, handcrafted levels. <br></li><li>Made a horrible mistake? No worries, use the <strong>undo button</strong>!<br></li><li>Turn-based traps and mechanics in Sokoban style puzzles.<br></li><li>Beat the devs and improve your best solutions with the<strong> step counter</strong>.<br></li><li>Three distinct worlds with environmental hazards like ice, falling rocks and of course: flamethrowers!<br></li><li>Can you find the ultra secret <strong>red coins</strong>?<br></li><li>Jump right into puzzle solving! No long cutscenes or tedious tutorials needed.<br></li><li>Levels get progressively more difficult as you progress through the worlds. <br></li><li>Play a game about robbing riches as a character named Rob Riches in a game called Rob Riches.</li></ul>",
